 ComicPress theme<br />\n* CSS mods and inclusions for the new ComicPress theme<br />\n* removed outdated -moz -webkit -khtml references in the CSS<br />\n* options added for landing pages and changing the default nav bar&#8217;s chapter navigation to go to it or not<br />\n* removed bad reference assignment &amp; in the buy-print shortcode<br />\n* revamped the query arguments in the thumbnail widget</p>\n<p>What needs tested?  Landing pages &amp; CSS changes</p>\n<p>Landing pages needs to be tested on working ComicPress themes out in the wild as well as non-comicpress themes to make sure that they work, or alternatively don&#8217;t work on those other themes.</p>\n<p>Please email me for information on how-to grab the pre-release version from the <a href=\"https://github.com/Frumph/comic-easel\" target=\"_blank\">github repo</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"http://comiceasel.com/2015/09/19/comic-easel-1-9-6-needs-testing/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"Comic Easel 1.9.4\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"http://comiceasel.com/2015/09/03/comic-easel-1-9-4/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\