;comic chapters&#8217; title if it&#8217;s empty</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Notes about Jetpack Mobile theme support:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>If you have your comic and/or comic blog not display on the home page of the normal theme, it won&#8217;t display on the home of the mobile theme, you will need to add a thumbnail widget to the mobile themes sidebar in the appearance -&gt; widgets</li>\n<li>big expansive lotsa buttons navigation do not look good, if you&#8217;re using the default, looks fine but if you&#8217;re using the graphic navigation with a ton of buttons .. no it won&#8217;t look good</li>\n<li>cannot remove the prev/next on the single pages of the comic in the mobile theme, the mobile theme is the problem with that one &#8211; no way to disable it without editing it&#8217;s source</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you find anything else wrong with the jetpack mobile theme stuff please comment and tell</p>\n<p>&#8212; Phil</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"http://comiceasel.com/2015/09/03/comic-easel-1-9-4/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"10\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"Comic Easel 1.9.3\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"http://comiceasel.com/201